Backend (Cloud Run):
- `DATABASE_URL` — Neon pooling connection string
- `GEMINI_API_KEY` — Google AI
- `ALLOWED_ORIGINS` — `https://udc-one.vercel.app`

Frontend (Vercel):
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_WQIS_API_URL` — Cloud Run service URL

## API Conventions
- All numeric sensor values must serialize to `float` in JSON (not `Decimal`)
- Timestamps must be ISO 8601, timezone-aware (`TIMESTAMPTZ`)
- CORS: allow `https://udc-one.vercel.app` and `http://localhost:3000`
- Health check: `GET /health` → `{"status": "ok"}` with HTTP 200

## Data Validation Rules
Parameter plausibility bounds:
- pH: 5.0–10.0 | Alert: < 6.5 or > 8.5
- Dissolved Oxygen: 0–20 mg/L | Alert: < 5.0
- Turbidity: 0–1000 NTU | Alert: > 50
- Temperature: 0–35°C | Alert: > 30
- Conductivity: 0–5000 µS/cm | Alert: > 1500

